Package gobblin.hive.metastore

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HiveMetaStoreBasedRegister
    An implementation of HiveRegister that uses IMetaStoreClient for Hive registration.
    HiveMetaStoreEventHelper
    Helper class to populate hive registration event in state.
    HiveMetaStoreUtils
    A utility class for converting Hive's Table and Partition objects into Gobblin's HiveTable and HivePartition objects, and vice versa.
